{"tid":2255212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無抑鬱症巴打分享下自己經歷？","createTime":"2020-10-23T11:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T15:23:00.000Z","uid":104309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6192f052054cabcb80c3431a15ff79cfba6d5770","tid":2255212,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:06:44.000Z","msg":"以前成日覺得人生係自己嘅意志力，但係我有焦慮症之後，我開始覺得好多野係人控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n焦慮症令我無時無刻個心都好緊張，一遇到問題，小至遲2分鐘到，個心就會那住那住。<br />\n遇到大少少嘅挫折就會開始諗未來都會一樣咁失敗，不如放棄左人生啦<br />\n<br />\n我有畏高，但近一年開始，我去到高處無驚不特止，反而好放鬆，覺得失足意外死係對身邊嘅人會係一個更好嘅交代。<br />\n<br />\n慢慢，到左後期，我幾個月完全無開心過，全日個心就好似登台一樣緊張，有胃痛嘅感覺。遲到就覺得處理唔到，日日諗咩死法舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n到上星期，見到iHerb 有隻藥可以平伏心情，鎮靜情緒<br />\n<br />\n成個人唔同左，個心真係無再痛，個人諗法完全唔同左。<br />\n之後上網睇先知有焦慮症<br />\n<br />\n有無抑鬱症巴打分享下自己經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75aeeef1996f66ee1b2ce24f32f206b734573b12","tid":2255212,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"有冇相似經歷嘅巴打？"},{"pid":"227d81834c78e7f0938f7302352312320bcd88e1","tid":2255212,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec1fbedafe29aa2c592be8a66c77b8eed6b8fee","tid":2255212,"uid":104309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /